npc.dialogs.Andre_0: <%s> Hello kiddo, I hope you are doing well.
npc.dialogs.Andre_1: <%s> Howdy, kiddo.  Searching for animal care supplies?  Iâ€™ve got 'em right here.
npc.dialogs.Bernina_0: <%s> Have you heard of the Elna fashion brand? My sister started that company!
npc.dialogs.Bernina_1: <%s> Now you look like a new hat would be just the thing to brighten up your day!
npc.dialogs.Elna_0: <%s> Hello %s! Care to try out some new looks today?
npc.dialogs.Elna_1: <%s> It would be amazing if we can have coordinated outfits for all the people in the settlement!
npc.dialogs.Fenny_1: <%s> I just came out a new plushy design today!  I hope you'll look forward to it whenever it goes on sale!
npc.dialogs.Harley:_0: <%s> Come get some of these arts and crafts to spread some holiday cheer!
npc.dialogs.Harley:_1: <%s> I really should practice my drums some more
npc.dialogs.Jess_0: <%s> The welcome center is getting more and more cozy everyday!  I love the updates you made to the place!
npc.dialogs.Jess_3: <%s> Oh oh! I think I just thought of another angle to advertize the adventure's settlement package!
npc.dialogs.Laly_0: <%s> Oooo do you have any minerals? I would love to process some for you!
npc.dialogs.Langley_0: <%s> Oh don't mind the smoke! I got everything under control!
npc.dialogs.Langley_1: <%s> ... ... Oh hi %s, was deep in thought there haha
npc.dialogs.Matan:_0: <%s> I've completed a new work today!  I hope you like to purchase a copy of it!
npc.dialogs.Matan:_1: <%s> Is there anything in my collection the piques your fancy?
npc.dialogs.Pamela_0: <%s> Hello %s have you discovered any interesting dishes recently?
npc.dialogs.Pamela_1: <%s> I wonder if my children back home would enjoy pork carrot wontons? Oh hello %s, how have you been?
npc.dialogs.Pamela_2: <%s> The place you've build for me is amazing! I love being able to cook while on my holiday!
npc.dialogs.Pamela_3: <%s> Do you need any common cooking ingredients?  I have plenty for sale!
npc.dialogs.Parlan_0: <%s> Hello %s I've got some new plumbing materials restocked today
npc.dialogs.Parlan_1: <%s> Need to repair your kitchen or bathroom? All my wares are of highest quality
npc.dialogs.Pengu_0: <%s> You should really check out Sky Penguins latest release Skye and I worked really hard on it.
npc.dialogs.Pengu_1: <%s> I wonder if we will be able to collab with Harley again soon?
npc.dialogs.Ren_1: <%s> Take good care of your tools
npc.dialogs.Rigg_0: <%s> You won't find this raccoon munching on miles tickets, no siree!
npc.dialogs.Rigg_1: <%s> Enchantment books, materials and collectible, I got it all right here!
npc.dialogs.Sam_0: <%s> Do you need any fishing equipment?  I've got you covered!
npc.dialogs.Sam_1: <%s> I've got to say it's very refreshing to sell sushi in this area
npc.dialogs.Sam_2: <%s> Have you caught anything interesting while fishing lately?
npc.dialogs.Skye_0: <%s> Hi %s, you got to check out these latest electronic releases!
npc.dialogs.Skye_1: <%s> I think you're office station could use a upgrade!
npc.dialogs.Skye_2: <%s> I just found a new supplier for amps, it's going to be very useful for our next Sky Penguins performance
npc.dialogs.Yukkie_0: <%s> Do you have any fruits on'ya?
npc.dialogs.Yukkie_1: <%s> Best thing to have after a long day of adventur'n is FRUIT!
